                     <interp inst="t18280221-168-person1024" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was sent for, and took the prisoner - he took his arm out of the sling, and struck me twice in the breast; he then ran away, but was taken in the street.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was intoxicated at the time.</p>
